{"title":"时间计算","time_limit":2000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2670","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>假设现在是2013年1月1日0:00分00秒，现在给出一个秒数S，求过S秒后时那年那月那日几时几分几秒.(设每月30天)</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>(多数据)  每行一个正整数S，当S=0时，输入结束。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p align=\"left\">每行以XnXyXrX:X:X(小时化为24小时制)</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n<p>100</p>\n<p>86400</p>\n<p>0</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2013n1y1r00:00:05</p>\n<p>2013n1y1r00:01:40</p>\n<p>2013n1y2r00:00:00</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>【数据范围】</p>\n<p>对于50%的数据  S≤20,000, 数据组数≤1000</p>\n<p>对于100%的数据  S≤100,000, 数据组数≤5000</p>\n<p>【提示】</p>\n<p>0:00:05按0: 0:5输出算错</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}